parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description: The time when the trace ends. The value is a timestamp. Unit: milliseconds.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The number of the page to return. Default value: `1`.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries to return per page, the maximum value is 1000.

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: The start time of the trace. The value is a timestamp. Unit: milliseconds.
